Black boots are armour pieces worn in the footwear slot. They require 10 Defence to wear.

One can obtain them as a drop from Bloodvelds, their mutated counterpart, their superior counterpart, or from trading with another player.

As with all metal boots and Black items, this piece of armour cannot be made using the Smithing skill.

''As with all [[metal boots]] and [[Black items]], this piece of armour '''cannot''' be made using the [[Smithing]] [[skill]].''
